announcements.name: Hypixel SkyBlock - 5th Anniversary
announcements.description: Hi SkyBlockers!  Today, we are celebrating the 5th Anniversary of Hypixel SkyBlock's release. It's been a long road since 2019, filled with many bumps and challenges.
